Changes since rc3 (the list may look long, but most are quite small corner cases):<br>
<br>
- Lots of threading fixes<br>
- More fixes for the new memory patcher system<br>
- Updates to NEWS and README<br>
- Fixed some hcoll bugs<br>
- Updates for external PMIx support<br>
- PMIx direct launching fixes<br>
- libudev fixes<br>
- compatibility fixes with ibv_exp_*<br>
- 32 bit compatibility fixes<br>
- fix some powerpc issues<br>
- various OMPIO / libnbc fixes from Lisandro Dalcin<br>
- fix some Solaris configury patching<br>
- fix PSM/PSM2 active state detection<br>
- disable PSM/PSM2 signal hijacking by default<br>
- datatype fixes<br>
- portals4 fixes<br>
- change ofi MTL to only use a limited set of OFI providers by default<br>
- fix OSHMEM init error check<br>
<br>
